column5: Went out at Sunset Bay....Walleyes are still there for the past two months. Got our twelve Walleyes in four hours. Dipseys, spinners w/worms are still the hot ticket. One on lead core. 70 to 73 feet is still hot. Not far from Canadian line.
jeez, you must eat well! nice job, early part of this week sure was beautiful wish I coulda gotten out like you!
